description:
&lt;p&gt;We have an exciting opportunity in Dermatology to become part of the waiting list co-ordinator team to be based at the Friends Dermatology Centre and the Kent and Canterbury hospital.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This is a new position to help schedule patients for their surgery dates, as well as work with the Dermatology team in achieving national and local targets.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The Friends Dermatology Centre is located at the Kent and Canterbury hospital within the 1937 building. The department has access to their own procedure rooms and a wide range of clinicians undertaking surgical lists. This is an exciting opportunity to join a flexible, dynamic and close working team.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;For further details / informal visits contact:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Name: Holly Groombridge, Job title: Operations Manager, Email address: holly.groombridge@nhs.net, Telephone number: 722 2108&lt;/p&gt;
